<plot>Singer Kitty Kallen has just threatened to quit her night club job unless the management provides her with a good accompanist. Enter Jan August, celebrated pianist, who, after playing "Besame Mucho" and "Jan's Boogie", gets the job. Miss Kallen also sings "Stardust". Three songs and plot development take only nine minutes.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?482229</url></doc>
